## Additional Notes

This project was developed for educational and portfolio purposes, demonstrating
end-to-end machine learning engineering practices applied to the Indian telecom
sector.

The dataset used in this project is synthetically generated to represent
realistic patterns in Indian telecom subscriber data. Any resemblance to actual
customer data of Reliance Jio, Airtel, Vodafone, or BSNL is coincidental.

